name: AVCaptureResolvedPhotoSettings
desc: A description of the features and settings in use for an in-progress or complete photo capture request.

items.name: uniqueID
items.desc: The unique identifier for the photo capture this settings object corresponds to.

items.name: expectedPhotoCount
items.desc: The number of photo capture results in the capture request.

items.name: isFlashEnabled
items.desc: A Boolean value indicating whether the camera flash will fire or has fired for this capture.

items.name: isStillImageStabilizationEnabled
items.desc: A Boolean value indicating whether this capture uses image stabilization.

items.name: isDualCameraFusionEnabled
items.desc: A Boolean value indicating whether this capture combines image data from a dual camera.

items.name: isRedEyeReductionEnabled
items.desc: A Boolean value indicating whether the camera automatically reduces red-eye when capturing photos.

items.name: photoDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the photo image (in a processed format such as JPEG) delivered by this capture.

items.name: rawPhotoDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the RAW-format photo image delivered by this capture.

items.name: previewDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the preview image delivered along with this capture.

items.name: embeddedThumbnailDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the thumbnail image delivered in this capture.

items.name: rawEmbeddedThumbnailDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the RAW-format embedded thumbnail image delivered by this capture.

items.name: livePhotoMovieDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the Live Photo movie content delivered by this capture.

items.name: portraitEffectsMatteDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the portrait effects matte delivered by this capture.

items.name: capturePhoto
items.desc: Initiates a photo capture using the specified settings.
